{"Id":477,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-anonymousgroupo","Author":"Anonymous Group Of Translators","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"Goodword Books , http://www.goodwordbooks.com/ , Center for Peace and Spirituality , https://www.cpsglobal.org/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"他曾皱眉，而且转身离去，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"因为那个盲人来到他 的面前。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你怎能知道呢？他也许能受薰陶，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"或听忠 告，而蒙教益。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"至于自满者，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你却逢迎他，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他不 受薰陶，于你何干？"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"至于殷切地来请教你，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"而且心怀 敬畏者，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"你却怠慢他。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"绝不然!这确是一种教训。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"谁欲记诵它，就叫谁记诵它吧。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"它在珍贵的册页 里；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"那些册页，是被称扬的，是被涤净的，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"是在许 多书记的手里的"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"那些书记，是尊贵的，是善良的。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"该死的人！他是何等的忘恩！"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"真主曾用什么创造 他的呢？"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"是用精液。他曾创造他，并预定他发育的程 序。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"然后，他使他的道路平易。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"然后，他使他死， 并安葬他。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"然后，当他意欲的时候，他使他复活。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"绝不然，他还没有奉行他所命令他的事务。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"教 人观察自己的食物吧！"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"我将雨水大量地倾注下来。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"然后，我使地面奇异地裂开，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"我在大地上生产百 谷，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"与葡萄和苜蓿，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"与榟橔和海枣，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"与茂密的 园圃，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"水果和牧草，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"以供你们和你们的牲畜享受。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"当震耳欲聋的轰声来临的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"在那日，各人将 逃避自己的弟兄、"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"自己的父母、"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"自己的妻子儿女"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"在那日，各人将自顾不暇；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"在那日，许多面目是光 华的，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"是喜笑的，是愉快的"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"在那日，许多面目上， 将有灰尘，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"黧黑将蒙蔽它。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"这等人，是不信道的， 是荒淫的。"}]}